            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner upon this charge at the 
               <persName id="t18150913-49-person462">
                  Brown 
                  Bear
               <interp inst="t18150913-49-person462" type="surname" value="Bear"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150913-49-person462" type="given" value="Brown"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150913-49-person462" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , opposite our office. He said, so help me God, George, you know I am not capable of such a thing. I searched him, but found nothing on him. I took<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181509130019"></xptr>him to the watchhouse, and knowing where he lived, I went to his lodgings, and there found the two duplicates, for the watch and seal, on the table.</p>
